OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome early morning cloud will
OL,6,Ftend to break up to leave a dry day
OL,7,Fwith warm sunny spells between
OL,8,Fvariable amounts of cloud. Gentle
OL,9,Fwinds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry with some late brightness
OL,12,Fthis evening. Argyll will have the
OL,13,Fbest of the sunny then clear spells,
OL,14,Fwhile the Glasgow area will become
OL,15,Fgenerally cloudier.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FDry and bright with
OL,18,Fvariable cloud. The best chance of
OL,19,Fbrighter or sunnier spells in the
OL,20,Fafternoon, particularly across Argyll.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
