OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FMainly dry and very warm on Thursday
OL,7,Fwith sunny spells. Cloudier, cooler on
OL,8,FFriday and Saturday with showery
OL,9,Foutbreaks of rain
